    <name>Ann Waggoner Hall</name>
    <description><![CDATA[Texas Wesleyan University,Ann Waggoner Fine Arts Building, northeast corner Wesleyan and E. Rosedale streets. https://txwes.edu/news-and-events/all-news/texas-sized-reputation/ann-waggoner-fine-arts-started-as-church-building/<br/><br/><b>Address:</b> 1309 Wesleyan Dr., Fort Worth]]></description>
    <Point><coordinates>-97.2806245725304,32.7310922776274,0</coordinates></Point>
